"2020-06-15T00:14:03.000Z","msg":"兩個都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinaarabcf.org/chn/zagx/zajw/t1784878.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinaarabcf.org%2Fchn%2Fzagx%2Fzajw%2Ft1784878.htm&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=1c7721ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinaarabcf.org/chn/zagx/zajw/t1784878.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦总统府发表声明支持中国维护主权安全和领土完整<br />\n  5月31日，驻巴勒斯坦办事处主任郭伟向巴官方报纸《新生活报》谈香港维护国家安全立法。<br />\n  郭伟表示，香港事务纯属中国内政，不容任何外部势力干涉。中国全国人大这一决定针对的是极少数严重危害国家安全的行为，不影响香港的高度自治，有助于维护香港居民的权利和自由，有助于保障外国投资者在港正当权益。<br />\n  郭伟表示，巴勒斯坦总统府昨天发表声明支持中国维护主权安全和领土完整，体现了两国高度的政治互信。支持中方维护主权、领土完整和国家安全是巴勒斯坦一贯立场，是中巴友好的必然结果。感谢巴方支持中方为保障包括香港在内的国家安全稳定所采取的立场和举措。香港国安立法必将发挥维护香港长治久安的关键作用。"},{"pid":"f1830929f8a2030b2e2a8f4a6e4a4d175cbf20a5","tid":2063647,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:17:45.000Z","msg":"抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefefa4eb557b2ca99e4cad24d821ca3e71c3dd9","tid":2063647,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981101e4a78457018c0a0c28b5000e774f8fddc8","tid":2063647,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9d0780de2a421d2bdd518ed8169c24f60b205c","tid":2063647,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a6b9d780deb9bddcfba2d4956cdb3f4780024d","tid":2063647,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T22:46:46.000Z","msg":"哦，老鳳用唔用係睇心情，關你撚事?<br />\n唔鍾意可以咪撚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T23:45:25.000Z","msg":"個個唔係巴基斯坦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:14:03.000Z","msg":"兩個都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinaarabcf.org/chn/zagx/zajw/t1784878.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li